{"tid":1418294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地要學共產黨果套, 學點樣去革命","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:32:44.000Z","uid":36092,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"16bc4bbf876ea44f643ad6c1f218af6e76ef8e58","tid":1418294,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/onazPF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FonazPF8.png&h=ebb1cfea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kf13H1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKf13H1b.png&h=9059162c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gsrjgmc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsrjgmc.png&h=b110fec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「人家打來了，我們就打，打是為了爭取和平」<br />\n「如果他們要打，就把他們徹底消滅」<br />\n<br />\n點解我地要勇武抗爭，因為要爭取五大訴求，要獲得香港的和平。點解我地會勇武，因為人地打我地先，所以我地要徹底消滅佢地。和理非、搵食撚、勇武撚、和平撚 we connect 呢個就係我地之後對抗中共港共既分化前中後線既分化策略，你識分化，我學返你果套 we learnt it<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">師赤共之技以制共</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"050ae99e0e9b20c2e7e634eea37d5c66b894de31","tid":1418294,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:22:38.000Z","msg":"五大訴求<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n4.追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f24f43280135b5627b29589845552a7b8a8388c5","tid":1418294,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df35a2c39d6932a3aa6e1589f4416e46ed3688a6","tid":1418294,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:40:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b46d829869d37b493514a52012e5862a6b0474e5","tid":1418294,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ac760c9825a2ffa6481b5c4e26537da9cf6123","tid":1418294,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}